Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial; font-size: 2.667rem; line-height: 1.31;\\\">脚手架基础1</h1><h1 data-v-3fbea7fe=\\\"\\\" class=\\\"article-title\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom: 1.667rem; color: rgb(37, 41, 51); font-weight: 600; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial; font-size: 2.667rem; line-height: 1.31;\\\"><div data-v-3fbea7fe=\\\"\\\" class=\\\"article-content\\\" itemprop=\\\"articleBody\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400;\\\"><div class=\\\"markdown-body\\\" style=\\\"word-break: break-word; line-height: 1.75; font-size: 16px; overflow-x: hidden;\\\"><p style=\\\"margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 22px; line-height: inherit;\\\">若只需要创建模板的功能，可以使用plop,yeoman这两个框架实现，或者利用create-react-app自定义模板。这些都是针对模板创建需求的高效方法。</p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 22px; line-height: inherit;\\\">本文讲解的是系统级的脚手架，包含模板创建，git-flow控制，cicd等功能。</p></div></div></h1><h2 data-id=\\\"heading-1\\\" style=\\\"margin-top: 35px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding-bottom: 12px; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(236, 236, 236);\\\">脚手架常见功能</h2><h1 data-v-3fbea7fe=\\\"\\\" class=\\\"article-title\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom: 1.667rem; color: rgb(37, 41, 51); font-weight: 600; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial; font-size: 2.667rem; line-height: 1.31;\\\"><div data-v-3fbea7fe=\\\"\\\" class=\\\"article-content\\\" itemprop=\\\"articleBody\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400;\\\"><div class=\\\"markdown-body\\\" style=\\\"word-break: break-word; line-height: 1.75; font-size: 16px; overflow-x: hidden;\\\"><ul style=\\\"padding-left: 28px;\\\"><li style=\\\"list-style: inherit;\\\">模板创建</li><li style=\\\"list-style: inherit;\\\">代码构建控制，如create-react-app中的webpack配置和eject,vue-cli的inspect等</li><li style=\\\"list-style: inherit;\\\">git-flow控制</li><li style=\\\"list-style: inherit;\\\">cicd</li></ul></div></div></h1><h2 data-id=\\\"heading-2\\\" style=\\\"margin-top: 35px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding-bottom: 12px; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(236, 236, 236);\\\">脚手架通用原理</h2><h1 data-v-3fbea7fe=\\\"\\\" class=\\\"article-title\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom: 1.667rem; color: rgb(37, 41, 51); font-weight: 600; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial; font-size: 2.667rem; line-height: 1.31;\\\"><div data-v-3fbea7fe=\\\"\\\" class=\\\"article-content\\\" itemprop=\\\"articleBody\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400;\\\"><div class=\\\"markdown-body\\\" style=\\\"word-break: break-word; line-height: 1.75; font-size: 16px; overflow-x: hidden;\\\"><blockquote style=\\\"margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 22px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); padding: 1px 23px; border-left: 4px solid rgb(203, 203, 203); background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\\\"><p style=\\\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: inherit;\\\">默认你已经学会操作系统的部分基础知识了，如果没有，遇到不会的请自学</p></blockquote><p style=\\\"margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 22px; line-height: inherit;\\\">举个例子: 在<code style=\\\"font-size: 0.87em; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; word-break: break-word; border-radius: 2px; overflow-x: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 245, 245); color: rgb(255, 80, 44); padding: 0.065em 0.4em;\\\">npm i -g @vue/cli</code>到<code style=\\\"font-size: 0.87em; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; word-break: break-word; border-radius: 2px; overflow-x: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 245, 245); color: rgb(255, 80, 44); padding: 0.065em 0.4em;\\\">vue create demo</code>，<code style=\\\"font-size: 0.87em; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; word-break: break-word; border-radius: 2px; overflow-x: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 245, 245); color: rgb(255, 80, 44); padding: 0.065em 0.4em;\\\">vue</code>这个命令为何能够执行。</p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 22px; line-height: inherit;\\\">先看<code style=\\\"font-size: 0.87em; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; word-break: break-word; border-radius: 2px; overflow-x: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 245, 245); color: rgb(255, 80, 44); padding: 0.065em 0.4em;\\\">npm i -g @vue/cli</code>后的目录结构：</p><pre style=\\\"font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; position: relative; line-height: 1.75; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\\\"><code class=\\\"copyable\\\" style=\\\"font-size: 12px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; word-break: normal; border-radius: 2px; overflow-x: auto; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; padding: 15px 12px; margin: 0px; display: block;\\\">/bin\\n  /vue 这个vue是软链接\\n/lib\\n  /node_module 这里是npm i -g后包存放的位置\\n    /@vue/cli\\n      /bin\\n        /vue.js\\n      /package.json\\n<span class=\\\"copy-code-btn\\\" style=\\\"position: absolute; top: 6px; right: 15px; line-height: 1; cursor: pointer; color: rgba(140, 140, 140, 0.8); transition: color 0.1s ease 0s;\\\">复制代码</span></code></pre><p style=\\\"margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 22px; line-height: inherit;\\\">下面是package.json部分代码</p><pre style=\\\"font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; position: relative; line-height: 1.75; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\\\"><code class=\\\"hljs language-js copyable\\\" lang=\\\"js\\\" style=\\\"font-size: 12px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; word-break: normal; border-radius: 2px; overflow-x: auto; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; padding: 15px 12px; margin: 0px; display: block;\\\">{\\n  <span class=\\\"hljs-string\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(221, 17, 68);\\\">\\\"bin\\\"</span>: {\\n    <span class=\\\"hljs-string\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(221, 17, 68);\\\">\\\"vue\\\"</span>: <span class=\\\"hljs-string\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(221, 17, 68);\\\">\\\"./bin/vue.js\\\"</span>\\n  }\\n}\\n<span class=\\\"copy-code-btn\\\" style=\\\"position: absolute; top: 6px; right: 15px; line-height: 1; cursor: pointer; color: rgba(140, 140, 140, 0.8); transition: color 0.1s ease 0s;\\\">复制代码</span></code></pre><p style=\\\"margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 22px; line-height: inherit;\\\">下面是/bin/vue的第一行代码</p><pre style=\\\"font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; position: relative; line-height: 1.75; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\\\"><code class=\\\"hljs language-js copyable\\\" lang=\\\"js\\\" style=\\\"font-size: 12px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; word-break: normal; border-radius: 2px; overflow-x: auto; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; padding: 15px 12px; margin: 0px; display: block;\\\"><span class=\\\"hljs-meta\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-weight: 700;\\\">#!/usr/bin/env node</span>\\n<span class=\\\"copy-code-btn\\\" style=\\\"position: absolute; top: 6px; right: 15px; line-height: 1; cursor: pointer; color: rgba(140, 140, 140, 0.8); transition: color 0.1s ease 0s;\\\">复制代码</span></code></pre><ol style=\\\"padding-left: 28px;\\\"><li style=\\\"padding-left: 6px; list-style: inherit;\\\"><code style=\\\"font-size: 0.87em; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; word-break: break-word; border-radius: 2px; overflow-x: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 245, 245); color: rgb(255, 80, 44); padding: 0.065em 0.4em;\\\">npm i -g</code>时，不仅会安装包到/lib/node_module下，还会解析@vue/cli/package.json，如果配置了bin，则会在/bin下创建对应的软链接，比如上述例子，软链接文件名则为vue,链接目标为@vue/cli/bin/vue.js</li><li style=\\\"padding-left: 6px; list-style: inherit;\\\">环境变量$PATH中配置了/bin对应的路径，所以在终端执行<code style=\\\"font-size: 0.87em; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; word-break: break-word; border-radius: 2px; overflow-x: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 245, 245); color: rgb(255, 80, 44); padding: 0.065em 0.4em;\\\">vue</code>时，就会找到/bin/vue文件，执行它，就相当于执行@vue/cli/bin/vue.js</li><li style=\\\"padding-left: 6px; list-style: inherit;\\\">vue.js是js文件，脱离js解释器是不可能直接执行的，在linux中，默认只会当成shell文件去执行。第一行<code style=\\\"font-size: 0.87em; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; word-break: break-word; border-radius: 2px; overflow-x: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 245, 245); color: rgb(255, 80, 44); padding: 0.065em 0.4em;\\\">#!/usr/bin/env node</code>，实际上就是shell语法，它的作用，就是将该文件托管到node去执行。</li></ol></div></div></h1><h2 data-id=\\\"heading-3\\\" style=\\\"margin-top: 35px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding-bottom: 12px; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(236, 236, 236);\\\">脚手架作用</h2><h1 data-v-3fbea7fe=\\\"\\\" class=\\\"article-title\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom: 1.667rem; color: rgb(37, 41, 51); font-weight: 600; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial; font-size: 2.667rem; line-height: 1.31;\\\"><div data-v-3fbea7fe=\\\"\\\" class=\\\"article-content\\\" itemprop=\\\"articleBody\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400;\\\"><div class=\\\"markdown-body\\\" style=\\\"word-break: break-word; line-height: 1.75; font-size: 16px; overflow-x: hidden;\\\"><p style=\\\"margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 22px; line-height: inherit;\\\">提升团队开发效率，如项目初始化模板，避免重复代码的编写，cicd等</p></div></div></h1><h2 data-id=\\\"heading-4\\\" style=\\\"margin-top: 35px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding-bottom: 12px; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(236, 236, 236);\\\">脚手架功能及分类</h2><h2 data-id=\\\"heading-5\\\" style=\\\"margin-top: 35px; margin-bottom: 1